### Get all todos
GET http://localhost:3000/todos

### Get one todos
GET http://localhost:3000/todos/1779449861912


### Create todo (valid request)
POST http://localhost:3000/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Learn NestJS",
  "completed": false
}


### Create todo (invalid - should fail validation)
POST http://localhost:3000/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": 123,
  "completed": "no"
}


### Create todo (missing field test)
POST http://localhost:3000/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Missing completed"
}